<h3 id="four-prayers">Four Prayers</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Search my <strong>heart</strong>.</li>
  <li>Reveal my <strong>fears</strong>.</li>
  <li>Uncover my <strong>sins</strong>.</li>
  <li>Lead me.</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="three-questions">Three Questions</h3>

<ol>
  <li>What are others trying to tell me?</li>
  <li>What have I rationalized for some time?</li>
  <li>Where am I most defensive?</li>
</ol>

<p>ÔøºÔøºÔøº<em>‚ÄúWhat we fear the most reveals where we trust God the least.‚Äù</em></p>

